Manufacturing Engineer- Dublin, Virginia
Commercial Vehicle Group is currently recruiting for a top-notch Manufacturing Engineer at our facility in Dublin, Virginia. In this role, the incumbent will have the following duties:

Responsible for implementation of assigned engineering and technical projects including required interaction with both internal and external personnel.
