CVG has established policies and practices supporting diversity. Company hiring decisions are based on merit, qualifications, experience and abilities. We are committed to non-discrimination in our employment practices without any regard to race, religion, gender, national origin, disability, sexual orientation, age, veteran or military status, pregnancy or any other basis prohibited by law.



