PROBLEM CONTROL SOP
This document is intended to provide users working knowledge of the Plex Problem Control system and processes they are expected to complete.  Plex is an online tool that can be accessed through any standard computer with internet access.
https://www.plexonline.com
TABLE OF CONTENTS
GETTING STARTED
Tips and Tricks
Supplier Management
Supplier Details and Contacts
Certification Management
Contact Management
PROBLEM CONTROL
