IT Budget




Commercial Vehicle Group specializes in building parts for heavy duty trucks, construction, agricultural, industrial and marine vehicles. Its division include its Interior Systems Division (Trim Systems, National Seating, and Cabarrus Plastics ) and Electrical Mechanical Division and Aftermarket group.
Corporate IT operations are led by the IT department centralized at the company headquarters in New Albany, OH with support staff at other plant locations. 

The Infrastructure & Security team handles daily IT operations, including infrastructure support and network operations.… MoreCorporate IT operations are led by the IT department centralized at the company headquarters in New Albany, OH with support staff at other plant locations. 

The Infrastructure & Security team handles daily IT operations, including infrastructure support and network operations. The Corporate IT Projects team leads the company IT initiatives, and is currently in the process of importing the company's .NET applications to SharePoint. The Systems Administration team is responsible for application and server upgrades at Commercial Vehicle Group.

On-site personnel manage daily IT operations and IT security at locations in Norwalk, OH and Kings Mountain, NC. The company employs Visage Mobile to provide mobile billing and inventory billing services.





